    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and minor dents, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. While the car is currently drivable, it may require some minor mechanical attention in the near future.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, providing a comfortable and reliable driving experience. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and all electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. While there are some minor exterior surface scratches consistent with careful use, the paint still holds a great shine. This car is ready for the road and would make an excellent choice for anyone seeking a dependable, quality vehicle without the price tag of a brand-new model.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and consistent operational reliability. The exterior maintains a professional aesthetic, while the interior remains refined and functional. For the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-caliber vehicle without the premium of a showroom-new price point, this offering represents an outstanding acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 29950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car, and I think you\u2019re going to absolutely love it! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is in really solid shape, perfect for everything from grocery runs to long weekend road trips. It runs like a charm and has been well-loved, so you can just hop in and go. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to start a new chapter with you. Drop me a message if you want to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically robust example of the marque\u2019s most celebrated chassis. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. While the exterior displays honest patina consistent with a well-driven car, the suspension geometry remains tight and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback enthusiasts crave. A visceral, driver-centric machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Reliable performance. Clean interior. Maintenance records available. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S, finished in a sophisticated Moonlight Blue Metallic. This vehicle offers a perfect blend of utility and sports-car DNA. The exterior retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find some typical road-wear including minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the lower rear valance. It sits on 19-inch staggered wheels with Michelin tires that have approximately 70% tread life remaining. Inside, the black leather interior is clean and smells fresh. The driver\u2019s side bolster shows some light softening and creasing from use, but the leather remains supple with no tears or punctures. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation, and heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the 3.0L Twin-Turbo V6 runs smoothly with no leaks or strange noises. The PDK transmission provides lightning-fast shifts, and the service history shows consistent oil changes and a recent brake fluid flush. This car has been a reliable daily driver and has never been tracked or abused. It comes with a complete set of floor mats, two key fobs, and the original manufacturer's literature.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience underpinned by mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. With a comprehensive service history and a focus on long-term reliability, this motorcar stands as a testament to quality engineering and responsible ownership.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that won't let you down? I\u2019m parting with my favorite car, and it's looking for a great new home! It\u2019s in wonderful shape, drives like a dream, and has been super well-loved. It's been a fantastic companion for my daily commutes and is ready for many more adventures with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Alpine White, a true driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This powerplant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Significant attention has been paid to the chassis; the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise damping and feedback characteristic of the M-division's engineering. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust and the cooling system has been overhauled for thermal efficiency. A mechanically sound, high-performance icon ready for the tarmac.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_8",
